## 1ï¸âƒ£ 1 Byte = 8 Bits

Haan, **1 byte me 8 bits hoti hain**.
Har bit 0 ya 1 ho sakti hai.

---

## 2ï¸âƒ£ Sab bits 1 ho â†’ kya hoga?

8-bit me agar **sab bits 1**:

```
