### ğŸ”¹ Summary Table

| Concept         | Bits | Max Value | Min Value |
| --------------- | ---- | --------- | --------- |
| 1 byte unsigned | 8    | 255       | 0         |
| 1 byte signed   | 8    | 127       | -128      |

